Package: Lujain
Type: Package
Title: The pachage allows the user to choose WDI series.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lujain Alsaleh
Maintainer: The package maintainer <lalsaleh@iu.edu>
Description: It allows the user who search about the public health to select series related
    to poverty and health equity, country or countries and years they are looking for. 
    The shiny gadget provides the user a scatter plot and a time plot, so they can 
    explore the series. 
